Jika ingin bilang sesuatu, katakanlah.

422
00:33:27,089 --> 00:33:28,090
Aku…

423
00:33:28,882 --> 00:33:30,175
Su-ryeon…

424
00:33:31,343 --> 00:33:32,845
Dia akan segera pulih.

425
